  "LIVERMORE_PIVOTS": {
    "_comment": "ATR multipliers for the Livermore State Machine (Phase 1). major_mult × ATR14 = pivot distance for MAIN state transitions. minor_mult × ATR14 = pivot distance for SECONDARY / bounce confirmation. dual_confirm = consecutive bars required to confirm a MAIN state flip. Calibrated on 4H data: BTC from BTC 4H (Jan2024–Feb2026, score=6.00/6), GOLD/FX defaults pending their own calibration runs.",
